ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations and Employment Board Act
SubjectOffice of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions of Canada - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving that the Office of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions ENTER INTO A COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada that covers all employees in the Professional Group bargaining unit for the period beginning on April 1, 2018 and ending on March 31, 2022 and is on the same terms and conditions as the previous collective agreement, except for the changes set out in the summary of changes.
